Lab 1 
a) Installation of Android Studio
b) Android Virtual Device Creation


Lab 2
a) Implement Hello World Program
b) Develop an android application to demonstrateActivity life cycle.


Lab 3
a) Develop an android application to demonstrate the Implicit and Explicit Intent.
b) Develop an android application to demonstrate Intent Filters


Lab 4
User Interface (UI) Layouts
a) Linear Layout, Relative Layout, Frame Layout, Table Layout, Constraint Layout
b) Web View, List View, Grid View


Lab 5
User Interface (UI) or Input Controls
a) TextView, EditText, Button, Toggle Button, CheckBox, Radiobutton, Spinner
b) DatePicker, TimePicker, SeekBar, RatingBar, TextClock, Switch


Lab 6
Menus
a) Options Menu,
b) Context Menu, Popup Menu


Lab 7
Android Notifications
a) Android Notifications (BigTextStyle,
BigPictureStyle, InboxStyle)
b) Android Custom Toast


Lab 8
Android Notifications
a) Android Progress Notification
b) Android Push Notification


Lab 9
Multimedia Components
a) Camera
b) Audio Player, Video Player


Lab 10
Develop an android application to implement login and registration screens.


Lab 11
Develop an android application to implement Android Tabs Layout.


Lab 12
Develop an android application using SQLite to perform CRUD Operations.

